    {
      "id": "4227ebad-b1de-4d81-b2d0-f7977c08e4d6",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Covid caused a massive transition to remote teaching platforms. The authors propose a ML algorithm called DeepLMS whose intent is to forecast the quality of interaction of the students with the LMS. Results show very small error between predictions and ground truth QoI. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "4227ebad-b1de-4d81-b2d0-f7977c08e4d6",
        "parent": {
